name: BOX Dude
description:
Zenshy's BOX Dude was created out of Bordeom, Obnoxiousness & Xhaustion.

Yes Zenshy can spell, he knows that Xhaustion is really spelt with an E as in 'Exhaustion' but he had to be creative when giving the word BOX an abbreviation.
This is the beginning of BOX Dude. Only 50 pieces of this specific BOX Dude will be given away on HEN and the other 50 put up for sale.

PS: BOX Dude is just as cool as Zenshy, he's just kinda mad at the moment
